///Create FTP Account in Cpanel///

1. go to Cpanel and login. Click on "FTP Accounts"
  a. Log in : info
	b. Domain: your domain name
	c. password: click on "Password Generator" 
	d. Directory: remove all from directory input box
	e. Quota: Unlimited
2. click on "Create FTP Account" button

///Copy FTP Account Info///
1. click on "Configure FTP Client" option in FTP Accounts
	
	FTP Username: info@woodyengineering.com 
	FTP server: ftp.woodyengineering.com 
	FTP & explicit FTPS port:  21 
	FTP password: your created password 

///Use FTP by use FileZila Client///
open FileZila software
	
	Host: FTP server name
	Username: FTP Username
	Password: FTP password
	Port: FTPS port

